tp://cfile7.uf.tistory.com/original/23605F4C56C8662A2AD5F5&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile7.uf.tistory.com/image/23605F4C56C8662A2AD5F5&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile4.uf.tistory.com/original/2224004C56C8662B0250AF&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile4.uf.tistory.com/image/2224004C56C8662B0250AF&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile21.uf.tistory.com/original/2357354C56C8662C2E1354&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile21.uf.tistory.com/image/2357354C56C8662C2E1354&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/original/2342894C56C8662D39CD4E&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/image/2342894C56C8662D39CD4E&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile30.uf.tistory.com/original/2569344C56C8662E258F3D&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile30.uf.tistory.com/image/2569344C56C8662E258F3D&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;수원 60년대 체험실 모퉁이에는 옛날 사진관이 있습니다. 이곳에서는 몇가지 옛날 의상을 입어보고 사진을 찍어 볼 수가 있습니다. 물론 입어보고 사진을 찍고 나서는 다음 사람들을 위해서 원래 위치에 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;잘 걸어두셔야 합니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&qu